{"tid":138244,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"係餐廳識左個大陸人妻 唔知食唔食到","createTime":"2017-02-28T12:19:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-11T01:01:26.000Z","uid":60123,"like":14,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ec8cbf32644545840d9d21a9f147926214cb713b","tid":138244,"uid":60123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T12:19:58.000Z","msg":"早幾日我買完野食 冇位 於是就唯有搭臺同人坐<br />\n<br />\n咁果到本身坐左個大陸人 一開始冇留意佢個樣 跟住食食下覺得佢都好似幾靚 聽到佢講電話用普通話 於是我就主動同佢講野<br />\n<br />\n然後講多兩句之後 佢話我講普通話都好標準 又想我幫佢個仔補習英文 於是佢主動同我交換左wechat<br />\n<br />\n我知佢老公係大陸做野多 幾個星期先見一次 佢話平時係香港都唔多野做 幾悶下<br />\n<br />\n不過暫時未夾到時間 所以未開始補習<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得我有冇機會食到佢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：真係有機會<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：慳d啦你 FF好啦"},{"pid":"73d4bc3db480729d1f305d3a95f89f0c84067a2d","tid":138244,"uid":19405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T12:23:44.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},{"pid":"9eb19603681f3ef2e205affeca5c844ce223ed75","tid":138244,"uid":82417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T12:38:21.000Z","msg":"人地仔都有個,就唔好搞事啦(我係佢老公切左你個春袋)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a4461ac3f956f729956d2117759b1516cd0747","tid":138244,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T13:04:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地仔都有個,就唔好搞事啦(我係佢老公切左你個春袋)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大陸雞"},{"pid":"5de074804fe3972ea01bd18197ac420f964cb021","tid":138244,"uid":26003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T13:08:29.000Z","msg":"真心幫個仔補習先，<br />\n同佢傾熟咗先睇吓佢咩approach"},{"pid":"da16efcb410ef6db609272de38e7c81c5a05c3a8","tid":138244,"uid":60123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T01:56:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心幫個仔補習先，<br />\n同佢傾熟咗先睇吓佢咩approach</blockquote><br />\n有冇d咩攻略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"febbb3e2eadfea487752b9045c40de49bfdfd459","tid":138244,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T02:08:16.000Z","msg":"比帽佢老公就啱啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇D大陸人落得嚟咁過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fbd526f9bbecd59ba7ad3ab7ae7573400c8007c","tid":138244,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T02:15:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/01/101542_ac36af704243437c562997891264e001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F01%2F101542_ac36af704243437c562997891264e001.jpg&h=73fba68b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33b225d245c01c515fc7b882c2d13e1be2d311de","tid":138244,"uid":60123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T03:25:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/01/101542_ac36af704243437c562997891264e001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F01%2F101542_ac36af704243437c562997891264e001.jpg&h=73fba68b&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁我一定唔夠佢有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc1e35c7edd775bb005c15b37ec20f060896c33b","tid":138244,"uid":35993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T04:22:03.000Z","msg":"分分鐘氹得佢高興佢俾零用你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45f333356ee094f4d04c6e39a690c0a000ae0edb","tid":138244,"uid":60123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T05:23:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分分鐘氹得佢高興佢俾零用你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockq